Author: CaterpillarTears
Text: I just love them. But I hate when people ask how I lost weight (I lost a huge amount) insert nervous laugh and "oh just eating less and exercise more".   Cut to me earing close to nothing and then everything around me and then purging it all out.  Yeah.

Author: elite-alien
Text: I fit into a size 6 a few weeks ago. Absolutely addicting.
